      "rationale": "Richardson extrapolation performed on three systematically refined meshes (2.1 M, 8.4 M, 33.6 M cells; refinement ratio 2). Grid convergence index (GCI) for NIH = 3.8 % on the medium mesh; GCI < 5 % acceptance criterion satisfied. Medium mesh (8.4 M) adopted for all production runs."
