      "rationale": "Benchtop hemolysis experiments conducted in phosphate-buffered saline with bovine blood at 37 °C ± 0.5 °C, haematocrit 33 ± 2 %. Flow rates set by calibrated Coriolis meter (±0.15 % FS). Rotational speed controlled by encoder feedback (±5 rpm). Experimental conditions documented in test plan TP-2022-07 and traceable to NIST standards."
