      "rationale": "NIH predictions compared against experimental measurements using area validation metric (AVM) and u-pooling. AVM score 0.82 (threshold 0.70). Prediction intervals computed via Monte Carlo UQ encompass 94 % of experimental observations. Systematic bias −2.1 % NIH is within experimental uncertainty band."
