      "rationale": "Validation experiments performed on the identical FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry at flow-speed combinations spanning the COU operating envelope (2 400–3 600 rpm, 2–8 L/min). Fluid properties, boundary conditions, and measurement quantities match COU specifications. Validation relevance score 0.91 on ASME V&V 40 Table 3 mapping."
