      "rationale": "Iterative convergence monitored via scaled residuals (< 1e-5 for all transport equations) and mass-flow imbalance (< 0.01 %). Round-off error estimated at machine epsilon × condition number; negligible relative to discretization error. Solver error budget < 0.5 % NIH, within acceptance threshold of 2 %."
    },
