      "rationale": "Simulation workflow executed by two independent analysts following documented simulation plan SP-2023-03. Independent parallel runs compared; NIH discrepancy < 0.3 %. Peer review of mesh, boundary conditions, and post-processing scripts completed by senior analyst. No use errors identified."
