      "rationale": "SST k-ω turbulence model selected based on published benchmark comparisons for confined rotating flows (Hariharan et al. 2011). Power-law hemolysis model (Giersiepen-Wurzinger coefficients) is the regulatory reference model. Model form uncertainty estimated via comparison with k-ε realizable variant; NIH difference 5.3 %, incorporated into UQ budget. Achieved level 3 reflects documented model-form uncertainty quantification."
    },
    {
