      "rationale": "Hemolysis experiments conducted with n = 5 independent blood batches per operating point (total 25 test runs). Sample size determined by power analysis (β = 0.80, α = 0.05) to detect 15 % NIH difference. Batch-to-batch variability (CV 8.3 %) incorporated into experimental uncertainty estimate. Samples traceable to lot records in laboratory notebook LN-2022-14."
