    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 ASME V&V 40 credibility factors have been assessed. In every case the achieved credibility level meets or exceeds the required level for Model Risk Level 3: Software QA (3≥2), Code Verification (3≥2), Discretization Error (3≥2), Test Conditions (2≥2), Output Comparison (3≥2), QoI Relevance (2≥2), Validation Relevance (3≥2), Solver Error (2≥2), Use Error (2≥1), Model Form (3≥2), Model Inputs (3≥2), Test Samples (2≥2), Input Equivalency (2≥2). Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification (n=2 000 LHS samples) has been performed and propagated through all three ValidationResult objects, each of which carries comparedAgainst, prov:wasGeneratedBy, and hasUncertaintyQuantification links. The provenance chain is complete from raw experimental datasets through validation activities to this UnitOfAssurance. No credibility gaps remain. The CFD hemolysis model is accepted for use in COU1 pump-characterisation decisions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump.",
    "decidedAt": "2026-04-19T00:00:00Z"
